Title: RSS-Include: false
RSS-Include: false

<p>
    This node has an <b>RSS-Include</b> header value of <i>false</i>.
</p>

<p>
    As a result, it is not eligible for inclusion in the
    generated RSS feed (<a href="{{rss:url}}">{{rss:url}}</a>).
</p>

<p>
    Most other nodes on this documentation site don&apos;t have the
    <b>RSS-Include</b> header set at all. As a result, they have the
    implicit default value of <i>false</i>, and are also not eligible
    for inclusion in the generated RSS feed.
</p>

<p>Compare this with {{node-link:headers/rss-include/true}}</p>
